sources.description:
Sheer horror as a living nightmare stalks the ocean floor!
A seaside community is terrorized by a hideous sea monster, which has been created by experiments in atomic radiation. Human bodies, charred and radioactive, begin to drift ashore.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/QoBLeGrdb4M


Original title: The Phantom from 10,000 Leagues (1955)

Writers: Lou Rusoff, Dorys Lukather
Stars: Kent Taylor, Cathy Downs, Michael Whalen
Genres: Classics, Cult Film, Horror, Sci-Fi
Budget: $100,000
